name: Myth Links
introduce: Myth Links is a three-match, card collection game with the background of Greek mythology and cyberpunk. Thanks to the  epic game story and different ways of playing, Myth Links' economic system contains a complete circle of buying, producing, consumption and earning. Meanwhile, its innovative POR(proof of ranking) token distribution model makes the possibility for all the active gamers to grow together, and it will put an end to scripts.
